{"about_the_game":"Magic Stone Guardians is a tower defense game that can be played in VR.<br>You play as a guardian deity protecting an underground temple and fight off enemies who try to steal the crystal.<br><br>Since the player is a spirit, he cannot attack the enemies directly.<br>Instead, they can summon Guardians by combining Magic Stones.<br><br>The combinations of strategies are endless with the combination and position of the Guardians to be summoned.<br>Use your own unique and powerful strategy to attack your enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Flow</h2>The game progresses in waves. When all enemies in a wave are defeated, the next wave begins.<br><br>The game incorporates a rogue light system.<br>If a crystal is destroyed, the game is over and progress is reset.<br><br>A boss wave will appear after every few normal waves.<br>Upon clearing the boss wave, players can choose one of the following rewards.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlock a usable cube.<br></li><li> Change the rate at which cubes are generated.<br></li><li> Raise the Guardian's level<br></li><li> build a cube generation platform.</li></ul><br>The sequence of steps up to this point is called a phase.<br>The game is completed when the boss of the final phase is defeated.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708750/extras/\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u306e\u6d41\u308c\u8aac\u660e\u753b\u50cf_en_640.png?t=1692242021\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How to battle</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Grab the Magic Stone<br>You can grab it by holding the pointer from your hand over the magic stone and pressing the trigger button.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708750/extras/\u30de\u30b8\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u30c8\u30fc\u30f3\u3092\u63b4\u3080__\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0_.png?t=1692242021\" /><br><br></li><li> Place the Magic Stone on the floor.<br>If you release the button while holding the magic stone, you can place it on the floor.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708750/extras/\u30de\u30b8\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u30c8\u30fc\u30f3\u3092\u7f6e\u304f__\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0_.png?t=1692242021\" /><br><br></li><li> Summon the Guardian<br>By placing white and other colored Magic Stones next to each other, you can summon a Guardian for that combination!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708750/extras/\u30ac\u30fc\u30c7\u30a3\u30a2\u30f3\u3092\u53ec\u559a__\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0_.png?t=1692242021\" /></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The First Step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/c73a257747dc1eb564b96b8edb8c30d6225953c8.jpg"},{"name":"Cannon Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/9c590fb590f9a51e0e73696d22d306da36dbabd0.jpg"},{"name":"Cannon Intermediate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/54401c27eff391750f9a795eae344f8eeb2087f8.jpg"},{"name":"Cannon Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/1e4b4d8ac3d827bd2824d063b526cd4096346e0c.jpg"},{"name":"Iron Pendulum Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/08876d7d1285a6b2403b9f8b2261017b5990dedc.jpg"},{"name":"Iron Pendulum Intermediate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/ad07697cb79a406d46ddfff6a0aee6cec93faa58.jpg"},{"name":"Iron Pendulum Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/43f4ad471d9e50e1d08257c772fea4fc41fb91e5.jpg"},{"name":"Heal Area Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1708750/1130c13c21d64b8cc86c799845fabbb3ea62cc09.jpg"},{"name":"Heal Area Intermediate